
Karwan Hedayat Trading Company(KHC)

Databse tables structure in KHC.



==> Models

    => User
        - ID
        - name
        - email
        - email_verified_at
        - password
        - rememberToken
        - profile_photo
        - role
        - timestaps

    => Post
        - ID
        - user_id
        - title
        - content

    => Tag
        - ID
        - post_id
        - tags

    

    => Image
        - ID
        - post_id
        - path
        - image

    => Slider
        - ID
        - text
        - image

    => Advertisement
        - ID
        - ads_photo

